description:
Join us as we continue this journey tracing our lineage, exploring the stories of Adam & Eve, Noah's Ark, and the flood. The father and mother of the first race were named Adam and Eve, they both started out life in the Garden of Eden. They encountered devastation within their family, due to their own perception of morality which had led to a terrible state of crime and violence. If they chose to continue with this way of life, God would cleanse the Earth with a flood. Following this, God instructed a man named Noah to build an ark...
